<item>
            <title>[LU-11502] add striped directory migration support in racer test</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11502</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Now only plain directory migration is tested  in racer.sh, the test script should be improved to support striped directory migration, and it should be stable, because after directory restripe support, it will become common to migrate striped directory on a system with other loads.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="53574">LU-11502</key>
            <summary>add striped directory migration support in racer test</summary>
